            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:2:2:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/24/2",
        "text": [
          " رِوَايَةِ عَمْرِو بْنِ جُمَيْعٍ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ قَالَ : \"غَبْنُ اَلْمُسْتَرْسِلِ رِبًا \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3983 - In a narration from Amr ibn Jameei, from Abu Abdullah (as), he said:\n\"Defrauding the one who entrusts you is usury.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2051,
        "local_index": 3,
        "narrator_chain": {
